<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10624535>
    dc:description "FIG. 12. — Distribution map for Warnstorfia fontinaliopsis (Müll.Hal.) Ochyra in the Danco Coast region. The position of this region in the Antarctic Peninsula is framed on the map (inset). The new locality on Murray (Bluff) Island is marked with a triangle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10624535/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10624538>
    dc:description "FIG. 13. — Distribution map for Warnstorfia fontinaliopsis (Müll.Hal.) Ochyra in the Graham Coast region and in the Antarctic Peninsula including the South Shetland Islands (inset). The new localities on Hovgaard Island and Barison Peninsula are marked with triangles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10624538/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

